            "🔧 `so_libs` — .so Native libraries\n"
            "🔤 `fonts` — TTF, OTF, WOFF\n"
            "🔒 `certs` — PEM, CER, Keystores\n"
            "📋 `configs` — JSON, YAML, Properties\n"
            "📝 `scripts` — JS, Python, Shell\n"
            "📄 `docs` — PDF, TXT, HTML\n"
